    "slug": "in-this-day-and-age-i-ask-anyone-i-date-right-away-are-you-married-are-you-i",
    "texto": "In this day and age, I ask anyone I date right away: 'Are you married? Are you in a relationship with anyone? Does anyone think they're in a relationship with you?' And by the way, if someone says, 'Yes, I am dating other people,' that's not necessarily a deal breaker. But you have to communicate it, not hide it.",
